16:53.440 --> 16:55.408
WE WERE SUPPOSED TO
BRING IT UP TO CHIP'S ROOM

16:55.410 --> 16:57.241
'CAUSE HE'S IN CHARGE
OF THE CASH.

16:57.250 --> 16:59.502
