TO SOMEONE?

20:04.630 --> 20:07.463
GO AHEAD,
SCREW YOUR BRAINS OUT.

20:16.810 --> 20:19.506
WHOA, WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR MITTS?

20:19.510 --> 20:21.512
