20:21.520 --> 20:23.681
I WAS WORKING THE BOO ROOM
AT THE HAUNTED HOUSE.

20:23.690 --> 20:26.909
BOO ROOM?
YOU KNOW, IT'S A STAPLE
OF HAUNTED HOUSES?

20:26.920 --> 20:29.559
IT'S PITCH-BLACK, WHERE
YOU DRESS LIKE CAT BURGLARS,

20:29.560 --> 20:30.879
JUMP OUT, YELL "BOO"?

20:30.890 --> 20:33.552
SO, YOUR HANDS ENDED UP
BRUISED HOW?

20:33.560 --> 20:36.757
I WAS CROUCHED DOWN, AND ONE
OF THE GUYS STOMPED ON THEM.

20:36.760 --> 20:38.466
HMM.

20:38.470 --> 20:40.768
