HUH? THAT BOY SCARES EASY.

20:53.250 --> 20:55.673
A PROBLEM IS JUST AN OPPORTUNITY
IN DISGUISE.

20:55.680 --> 20:57.614
TELL ME WHO YOU WERE WITH,
I'LL CONFIRM IT,

20:57.620 --> 20:59.281
AND YOU'RE IN THE CLEAR.

20:59.290 --> 21:00.917
NO, I'M NOT.

21:00.920 --> 21:02.956
SEE, I COULD TELL YOU,
BUT THE GIRL I WAS WITH

21:02.960 --> 21:06.726
WOULD NEVER IN A MILLION YEARS
ADMIT TO IT.

21:10.500 --> 21:12.388
OKAY, I GOT TO GO.

21:12.400 --> 21:14.766
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:17.070 --> 21:21.530
IT'S SAD TO SEE HIM GO, BUT
IT'S NICE TO WATCH HIM LEAVE.

21:21.540 --> 21:23.076
DO I KNOW YOU?

21:23.080 --> 21:25.378
OH, I'M FRIENDS WITH YOUR
BOYFRIEND, CHARLESTON,

21:25.380 --> 21:27.678
AND YOUR BOY
ON THE SIDE, CHIP.

21:27.680 --> 21:30.319
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

21:30.320 --> 21:31.878
YOU AND CHIP.

21:31.890 --> 21:33.653
