TO THE HAUNTED HOUSE?

21:33.660 --> 21:35.582
I HEAR YOU WENT AS THE BEAST
WITH TWO BACKS.

21:35.590 --> 21:37.558
NO, WHY WOULD
YOU EVEN SAY THAT?

21:37.560 --> 21:39.687
LOOK, YOU'RE CHIP'S ALIBI.

21:39.690 --> 21:41.851
