27:38.590 --> 27:40.148
CAN I TALK TO YOU?

27:40.150 --> 27:42.789
YOU A LITTLE BUSY DOING
FUNNEL SHOTS WITH THE PI SIGS?

27:42.790 --> 27:44.121
AREN'T YOU?

27:44.130 --> 27:46.086
I HEARD YOU WENT
TO THEIR HAUNTED HOUSE.

27:46.090 --> 27:48.320
THAT MUST HAVE BEEN FUN.
DID YOU GO AS A HYPOCRITE?

27:48.330 --> 27:51.026
I WENT WITH CLAIRE BECAUSE WE
HEARD THERE WAS A GROPE ROOM.

27:51.030 --> 27:53.897
AND YOU WERE LOOKING
FOR A LITTLE GRAB-ASSING?

27:53.900 --> 27:55.765
A LITTLE POETIC JUSTICE.

27:56.440 --> 27:59.364
THEY SET UP THIS BOO ROOM
SO THEY COULD FONDLE GIRLS

27:59.370 --> 28:01.736
AS THEY WENT THROUGH,
SO WE DRESSED UP AS RATS

28:01.740 --> 28:04.743
AND STRATEGICALLY PUT RAT TRAPS
ON ALL OF OUR GROPEABLE PARTS.

28:04.750 --> 28:07.401
OKAY,
THAT IS PRETTY GENIUS.

28:07.410 --> 28:09.241
I WAS IN THE ROOM
ALL OF THREE SECONDS

28:09.250 --> 28:11.912
BEFORE DICK CASABLANCAS
WAS CAUGHT IN ONE OF MY TRAPS.

28:11.920 --> 28:14.252
THEIR BRUISED HANDS.

28:14.260 --> 28:17.309
IT MUST HAVE HURT -- HE RAN
ME OUT OF THE PARTY, SCREAMING.

28:17.320 --> 28:19.026
WAS CLAIRE WITH YOU?

28:19.030 --> 28:22.420
NO. THAT'S WHEN
I LOST TRACK OF HER.

28:22.430 --> 28:25.297
I LOOKED FOR HER FOREVER, AND
I THOUGHT I SAW HER LATER ON,

28:25.300 --> 28:27.621
DOWN THE STREET FROM THE PARTY,
BUT IT WASN'T HER.

28:27.630 --> 28:29.268
YOU'RE SURE?
YEAH.

28:29.270 --> 28:31.363
I YELLED FOR HER.
NOTHING.

28:31.370 --> 28:34.168
THE SHERIFF
KNOWS ALL OF THIS.

28:34.180 --> 28:38.241
SO, THE GIRL YOU THOUGHT WAS
CLAIRE, WHERE DID YOU SEE HER?

28:38.250 --> 28:40.377
NANCY THOUGHT SHE SAW CLAIRE
ON THE STREET

28:40.380 --> 28:42.348
OUTSIDE OF THIS
CONVENIENCE STORE.

28:42.350 --> 28:46.741
IT'S WORTH MAKING SURE SHE
WASN'T RIGHT THE FIRST TIME.

28:46.750 --> 28:49.082
HI, I WAS WONDERING --
I'M NOT HIRING.

28:49.090 --> 28:51.058
ACTUALLY, I WAS WONDERING

28:51.060 --> 28:53.381
IF YOU WERE WORKING
LAST SATURDAY NIGHT.

28:53.390 --> 28:55.051
I WORK EVERY SATURDAY NIGHT.

28:55.060 --> 28:56.698
WHAT ELSE AM I GONNA DO?

28:56.700 --> 29:00.067
DO YOU REMEMBER
SEEING THIS GIRL?

29:00.070 --> 29:01.537
HER NAME IS CLAIRE.

29:01.540 --> 29:04.202
YEAH, I SAW HER.
SO DRUNK SHE COULD BARELY STAND.

29:04.210 --> 29:07.008
IF YOUR PARENTS KNEW WHAT
YOU KIDS REALLY DO HERE...

29:07.010 --> 29:09.774
AND YOU'RE SURE IT WAS HER?

29:09.780 --> 29:11.941
SHE CAME IN WITH A GUY.

29:11.950 --> 29:14.214
SHE'S FALLING ASLEEP
ON MY MAGAZINE RACK.

29:14.220 --> 29:16.916
HE'S TRYING TO SCRAPE TOGETHER
CHANGE TO BUY PROPHYLACTICS.

29:16.920 --> 29:20.048
THEN, HE'S ALL MAD BECAUSE
HE CAN'T USE A CREDIT CARD

29:20.050 --> 29:22.211
UNLESS HE SPENDS $15.

29:22.220 --> 29:24.882
SO I SENT HIM NEXT DOOR
TO THE ATM.

29:24.890 --> 29:26.824
THEY CAME BACK LATER.

29:26.830 --> 29:28.195
HE BOUGHT HIS RAINCOAT.

29:28.200 --> 29:31.897
ONE LESS BASTARD CHILD
CONCEIVED BY MORONS.

29:33.100 --> 29:35.432
EVERYONE'S HAPPY.

29:37.340 --> 29:39.467
THAN KS.

29:39.470 --> 29:42.974
I STARTED BUGGING MY MOM ABOUT
WHO MY DAD WAS WHEN I WAS,

29:42.980 --> 29:45.107
I DON'T KNOW, 6, 7.

29:45.110 --> 29:47.249
THEN, ON MY 10th BIRTHDAY,
MY MOM TAKES ME

29:47.250 --> 29:49.377
TO SEE AARON ECHOLLS
IN "THOUGHT POLICE."

29:49.380 --> 29:51.439
SHE POINTS TO THE SCREEN,
SHE SAYS,

29:51.450 --> 29:53.441
"THAT'S THE GUY.
THAT'S YOUR DAD."

29:53.450 --> 29:56.112
SHE TOOK YOU TO SEE "THOUGHT
POLICE" ON YOUR BIRTHDAY?

29:56.120 --> 29:57.781
DID SHE HATE YOU?

29:57.790 --> 29:59.348
[ LAUGHS ]

29:59.360 --> 30:01.954
I'M LIKE, "MOM, DON'T SCREW
WITH MY HEAD. I'M 10.

30:01.960 --> 30:03.427
"I CAN'T DEAL WITH THE NEWS

30:03.430 --> 30:05.421
"THAT THE GUY MIND-WRESTLING
WITH STALLONE ON-SCREEN

30:05.430 --> 30:07.022
KNOCKED YOU UP."

30:07.030 --> 30:09.430
SHE WAS A STEWARDESS
WHEN SHE MET AARON.

30:09.440 --> 30:11.260
SHE SAID SHE MET HIM
WORKING FIRST CLASS

30:11.270 --> 30:13.875
ON AN
L.A.-TO-NEW-YORK RED-EYE.

30:13.880 --> 30:15.131
MY MOM IS A LOOKER.

30:15.140 --> 30:17.802
YEAH, I'M SURE SHE IS.

30:17.810 --> 30:21.018
I DIDN'T BELIEVE HER TILL
SHE SHOWED ME THE HUSH MONEY.

30:21.020 --> 30:23.716
HOW MANY KIDS OF SINGLE-PARENT
FLIGHT ATTENDANTS

30:23.720 --> 30:25.381
GO TO THE BEST
PRIVATE SCHOOLS?

30:25.390 --> 30:27.540
STILL, I'D SEE PICTURES
OF YOUR FAMILY AND THINK,

30:27.550 --> 30:29.154
"THAT LIFE SHOULD BE MINE."

30:29.160 --> 30:31.424
EH, YOU DON'T WANT IT.
TRUST ME.

30:31.430 --> 30:33.421
NO, I KNOW.
THAT'S THE THING.

30:33.430 --> 30:35.796
THE MORE I WATCHED, THE HAPPIER
I WAS THAT IT WASN'T MY FAMILY.

30:35.800 --> 30:39.588
YOUR DAD CHEATS ON YOUR MOM,
IT'S ON THE COVER OF PEOPLE.

30:39.600 --> 30:41.488
YOUR SISTER SHOOTS NICOLE RICHIE
WITH A B.B. GUN,

30:41.500 --> 30:43.730
JAY LENO OPENS HIS MONOLOGUE
WITH IT.

30:43.740 --> 30:45.298
THEN THE MURDER.

30:45.310 --> 30:47.107
I STARTED WONDERING IF SOMETHING
WAS WRONG WITH ME,

30:47.110 --> 30:48.873
YOU KNOW,
IF THIS IS MY BLOODLINE.

30:48.880 --> 30:52.247
YEAH, JOIN THE CLUB.

30:52.250 --> 30:54.309
WELL...

30:54.320 --> 30:57.016
THIS HAS BEEN GREAT, BUT
I GOT TO RUN -- PAPERS TO GRADE.

30:57.020 --> 30:58.544
OH, YEAH.

30:58.550 --> 31:03.283
THAT IS, WE'LL HAVE TO DO IT
AGAIN -- LONGER, NEXT TIME.

31:03.290 --> 31:04.723
YEAH.

31:04.730 --> 31:07.085
I'D LIKE TO HEAR ABOUT HIM,
THE DETAILS, GOOD OR BAD.

31:07.090 --> 31:08.523
YEAH, BAD, MOSTLY.

31:08.530 --> 31:11.988
THERE'S JUST THIS VOID,
YOU KNOW.

31:12.000 --> 31:14.468
OH, HELLO.

31:14.470 --> 31:17.359
VERONICA, THIS IS MY
HALF-BROTHER, CHARLIE.

31:17.370 --> 31:19.338
CHARLIE,
MY GIRLFRIEND, VERONICA.

31:19.340 --> 31:21.706
HEY,
NICE TO MEET YOU.

31:21.710 --> 31:23.940
YEAH, YOU TOO.

31:23.950 --> 31:26.271
WELL, CHARLIE HAS TO GET HOME,
GRADE PAPERS.

31:26.280 --> 31:27.679
HE'S GOT AN HONEST JOB.

31:27.680 --> 31:30.069
HE'S A CONTRIBUTING
MEMBER OF SOCIETY.

31:30.080 --> 31:31.513
VERY UN-ECHOLLS.

31:31.520 --> 31:33.613
YEAH, AND IF I GET THEM
GRADED BY TONIGHT,

31:33.620 --> 31:35.485
I CAN HIT ZUMA AT DAWN.

31:36.420 --> 31:37.819
YOU SURF?

31:37.820 --> 31:40.129
AS OFTEN
AND AS LONG AS I CAN.

31:40.130 --> 31:43.520
MAN, WE ARE BROTHERS.

31:49.840 --> 31:51.467
I HAVE OPTIONS.

31:51.470 --> 31:53.438
I COULD BE EXCITED FOR LOGAN --
THRILLED, EVEN --

31:53.440 --> 31:58.139
THAT HIS NEW BROTHER IS SUCH
A KEEPER, OR I CAN BE ME.

32:08.460 --> 32:11.520
HI, UH,
SORRY TO BOTHER YOU.

32:11.530 --> 32:14.499
ARE YOU, BY ANY CHANCE,
THE SUB FOR MR. STONE?

32:14.500 --> 32:17.719
NO, I'M THE REAL DEAL.
I'M MR. STONE.

32:18.600 --> 32:20.966
SORRY,
I'VE GOT A CLASS STARTING.

32:20.970 --> 32:22.369
DID YOU NEED SOMETHING?

32:22.370 --> 32:24.406
NO, UH...

32:24.410 --> 32:26.264
JUST LOOKING
FOR SOMEONE ELSE.

32:26.270 --> 32:29.433
OKAY,
THEN I GOT TO CALL ROLL.

32:39.190 --> 32:40.589
IT'S CHRISTMAS, RIGHT?

32:40.590 --> 32:46.153
THE ENTIRE FAMILY UNIT
IS AROUND, WHICH WAS RARE.

32:46.160 --> 32:49.493
AND I'M, I DON'T KNOW, 9.

32:49.500 --> 32:52.060
AND AARON HANDS ME A GIFT,
YOU KNOW.

32:52.070 --> 32:55.892
BUT HE NOTICES THE BOX HAS BEEN
REWRAPPED, SO HE KNOWS I PEEKED.

32:55.900 --> 33:00.269
I'M 9 YEARS OLD. HE'S REGIFTING
ME A FRUIT BASKET.

33:00.270 --> 33:03.000
HE STARTS SHOUTING
ABOUT HOW I RUINED CHRISTMAS.

33:03.010 --> 33:05.069
OH, MY GOD.

33:05.080 --> 33:08.572
THEN HE TELLS ME
I'M NOT OPENING ANOTHER GIFT

33:08.580 --> 33:11.014
UNTIL I EAT ALL 12 PEARS
IN THE BOX.

33:11.020 --> 33:12.817
DAMN, MAN,
THE SCISSORS INCIDENT,

33:12.820 --> 33:15.948
DRAINED SWIMMING POOL EPISODE,
NOW THE BOX OF PEARS.

33:15.960 --> 33:17.689
SO, I'M EATING THE PEARS.

33:17.690 --> 33:21.251
I'M TAKING MY TIME,
TAKING THESE DAINTY BITES.

33:23.760 --> 33:26.297
THE MAN COMES UNHINGED.

33:27.730 --> 33:30.893
HE TAKES THESE PEARS AND STARTS
SHOVING THEM DOWN MY THROAT,

33:30.900 --> 33:32.231
ONE AFTER ANOTHER.

33:32.240 --> 33:35.903
AND I'M CHOKING,
BUT HE DOESN'T STOP

33:35.910 --> 33:39.573
UNTIL MY MOM HOLDS
A CHEESE KNIFE TO HIS THROAT.

33:39.580 --> 33:42.344
TO THIS DAY,
I PUKE IF I SMELL A PEAR.

33:45.050 --> 33:48.451
AAH!

33:57.130 --> 34:00.065
QUICK, JIM,
HIDE THEM HOOKERS.

34:00.070 --> 34:02.038
HMM.

34:04.410 --> 34:07.436
HI, LOGAN.
HI, NORMAN PHIPPS.

34:08.340 --> 34:10.308
WHAT'D YOU CALL HIM?

34:10.310 --> 34:12.403
HIS NAME -- NORMAN PHIPPS.

34:12.410 --> 34:15.618
AT LEAST, THAT'S THE NAME OF THE
GUY WHO RENTED HIS RENTAL CAR.

34:15.620 --> 34:18.509
AND A QUICK GOOGLE CHECK
REVEALS THAT NORMAN PHIPPS

34:18.520 --> 34:20.545
IS A CONTRIBUTOR
TO VANITY FAIR.

34:20.550 --> 34:23.018
THANK GOD
FOR MOBILE WIRELESS, HUH?

34:23.020 --> 34:25.818
SO, NORMAN,
HOW'S YOUR STORY COMING?

34:25.830 --> 34:27.855
IT'S GREAT.

34:27.860 --> 34:29.919
IN FACT, I'M ALMOST THERE.
JUST ONE THING, LOGAN.

34:29.930 --> 34:32.763
THAT FRUIT BASKET,
WAS IT FROM HARRY AND DAVID?

34:32.770 --> 34:34.328
GOD IS IN THE DETAILS.

34:34.940 --> 34:39.138
OH, PLEASE TAKE A SWING.
IT'D MAKE A GREAT LEAD.

34:42.640 --> 34:44.176
[ GASPS ]

34:45.680 --> 34:49.343
I'M SO SORRY. I SHOULD HAVE
JUST LEFT IT ALONE.

34:53.890 --> 34:58.384
WELL, THEN, I GUESS
THIS IS THE MONEY SHOT, RIGHT?

35:00.160 --> 35:03.459
I WANTED PROOF,
I GOT PROOF.

35:03.460 --> 35:05.963
SO NOW I DO IT, RIGHT,
I LEAVE HIM?

35:05.970 --> 35:07.926
HARMONY.
IS THAT STANDARD
OPERATING PROCEDURE?

35:07.930 --> 35:10.535
I MEAN, DO I KICK HIM OUT?
WOULD HE MOVE OUT?

35:10.540 --> 35:12.565
DO I TAKE OUR DAUGHTER
TO A HOTEL?

35:12.570 --> 35:15.175
HARMONY,
BEFORE YOU DO ANYTHING...

35:19.010 --> 35:21.240
...YOU NEED TO HEAR THIS.

35:22.650 --> 35:24.447
Marvin:
He's one of those people.

35:24.450 --> 35:27.248
He thinks the years he's logged
are in direct proportion

35:27.250 --> 35:29.013
to how smart --

35:29.020 --> 35:32.057
Oh, wait, Carly, stop.

35:32.060 --> 35:33.425
I can't.

35:33.430 --> 35:35.398
I have a wife, a family.

35:35.400 --> 35:37.027
I'm not going to do this.

35:37.030 --> 35:38.395
THEY LEFT SEPARATELY.

35:38.400 --> 35:40.925
I FOLLOWED MARVIN
BACK TO YOUR HOUSE.

35:40.930 --> 35:43.831
THIS MORNING, HE HANDED OFF
THE REILLY INTERNATIONAL ACCOUNT

35:43.840 --> 35:49.437
TO SOMEONE NAMED
DARRELL DERRYBERRY.

35:50.910 --> 35:53.140
I SHOULD GO HOME.

35:55.320 --> 35:57.538
YES, YOU SHOULD.

36:16.100 --> 36:18.898
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

36:20.240 --> 36:22.333
REMEMBER THAT CASE
A COUPLE YEARS AGO

36:22.340 --> 36:24.843
WHERE THAT WOMAN WAS
IMPERSONATING HER BOSS?

36:24.850 --> 36:29.219
HOW DID YOU "OBTAIN"
THE ATM PHOTOS THAT PROVED IT?

36:29.220 --> 36:30.710
I KNOW A GUY.

36:31.820 --> 36:35.312
A REPRESENTATIVE OF THE BANK
NEEDS TO REQUEST A COURT ORDER,

36:35.320 --> 36:37.356
AND ONCE THE COURT ORDER
IS ISSUED,

36:37.360 --> 36:39.885
IT ONLY TAKES ABOUT
AN HOUR TO GET THE PHOTOS.

36:39.890 --> 36:41.551
SO IT'S A PIECE OF CAKE?

36:41.560 --> 36:44.961
A MONKEY WITH A FRIEND WHO'S
A BANK REPRESENTATIVE CAN DO IT.

36:44.970 --> 36:50.169
SO, BUBBLES, YOU FEEL LIKE
DOING ME A SOLID?

36:50.170 --> 36:52.263
HMM?

36:58.450 --> 37:02.910
HELLO, CHIP, DICK, FACELESS
"STAR TREK" CREW MEMBERS.

37:02.920 --> 37:05.548
HEY, GONNA GIVE US
OUR MONEY BACK?

37:05.550 --> 37:06.619
HMM.

37:06.620 --> 37:08.315
THE MORNING
AFTER THE HAUNTED HOUSE,

37:08.320 --> 37:10.754
CLAIRE WOKE UP ALONE
IN THE PARK, 5:00 A.M.

37:10.760 --> 37:12.057
HER HEAD WAS SHAVED.

37:12.060 --> 37:15.359
THIS PHOTO WAS TAKEN OF CLAIRE
THE NIGHT SHE WAS RAPED.

37:15.360 --> 37:17.794
IT'S FROM AN ATM ON THE CORNER
OF STANTON AND LAKE.

37:17.800 --> 37:20.826
LOOK AT THE TIME STAMP --
2:00 A.M.

37:20.830 --> 37:23.196
THE HAUNTED HOUSE HAD BEEN
CLOSED FOR TWO HOURS.

37:23.200 --> 37:25.907
SHE STILL HAS HER HAIR, SO WE
KNOW SHE HASN'T BEEN RAPED YET.

37:25.910 --> 37:27.901
AND LOOK WHO SHE'S WITH.

37:27.910 --> 37:30.276
WHO'S THAT DUDE?
IT'S NOT ONE OF US.

37:30.280 --> 37:31.645
PRECISELY.

37:31.650 --> 37:34.005
YOU PI SIGS HAVE EXACTLY
ONE ASIAN MEMBER,

37:34.010 --> 37:35.568
AND THAT'S NOT HIM.

37:35.580 --> 37:38.140
VOIL, PROOF OF INNOCENCE,

37:38.150 --> 37:41.415
COURTESY OF PIXIE SPY MAGIC.

37:41.420 --> 37:43.684
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:49.500 --> 37:53.493
HMM, WHEN DID THE GREEK CHORUS
OF FEMINIST SHAME ARRIVE?

37:53.500 --> 37:55.764
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

37:57.100 --> 37:58.704
STOP FOR A PICTURE, CHARLIE!

37:58.710 --> 38:02.430
CHARLIE, TELL US
ABOUT LOGAN ECHOLLS!

38:02.440 --> 38:04.305
CHARLIE! CHARLIE!

38:04.310 --> 38:06.175
STOP FOR A PICTURE,
COME ON!

38:06.180 --> 38:08.614
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

38:11.750 --> 38:13.047
GOOD NEWS.

38:13.050 --> 38:14.859
THE PI SIGS WERE ABSOLVED.

38:14.860 --> 38:16.953
BECAUSE THEY WERE INNOCENT,
PARKER.

38:16.960 --> 38:18.450
BECAUSE YOU HELPED THEM,

38:18.460 --> 38:21.179
WHICH IS WHAT YOU WERE TRYING
TO DO ALL ALONG.

38:21.190 --> 38:22.589
HOW DO YOU
LIVE WITH YOURSELF?

38:22.600 --> 38:26.422
I WAS LOOKING FOR THE TRUTH,
AND I FOUND IT.

38:26.430 --> 38:28.295
YOU WANT TO NAIL
SOMEONE TO THE WALL

38:28.300 --> 38:29.938
JUST TO HAVE SOMEONE
NAILED THERE,

38:29.940 --> 38:32.408
OR DO YOU WANT THE PERSON
RESPONSIBLE TO PAY?

38:43.420 --> 38:46.617
HEY, CAREFUL, MAN,
THERE'S A BEVERAGE HERE.

38:46.620 --> 38:48.713
YOU DOING OKAY?

38:48.720 --> 38:51.314
ON TOP OF THE WORLD,
LOOKING DOWN ON CREATION.

38:51.320 --> 38:53.629
I SAW YOU ON "LARRY KING"
LAST NIGHT,

38:53.630 --> 38:56.952
GIVING YOUR HALF-BROTHER
A LITTLE COMING-OUT PARTY.

38:56.960 --> 38:59.520
LIFE AS CHARLIE STONE KNEW IT
IS OFFICIALLY OVER.

38:59.530 --> 39:02.135
[ Sarcastically ]
I'M CHOKING WITH EMPATHY.

39:02.140 --> 39:04.358
BY SERVING UP THAT
VANITY FAIR REPORTER,

39:04.370 --> 39:05.906
HE BROUGHT IT ON HIMSELF.

39:05.910 --> 39:08.504
WELL, WE DON'T KNOW
THAT FOR SURE.

39:08.510 --> 39:11.809
WELL, HOW ELSE
COULD IT HAVE HAPPENED?

39:11.810 --> 39:13.346
[ SIGHS ]

39:13.350 --> 39:15.170
WELL,
I'M GLAD YOU WENT DIGGING.

39:15.180 --> 39:18.240
I MEAN, IT OFFICIALLY ERASED
ANY AND ALL ROMANTIC NOTIONS

39:18.250 --> 39:20.286
ABOUT MY FAMILY.

39:20.290 --> 39:22.656
THAT'S ME,
ALL SORTS OF HELPFUL.

39:22.660 --> 39:24.924
I WAS HOPING YOU COULD
BUST SOME OF IT OUT AGAIN

39:24.930 --> 39:26.818
AND HELP ME FIND
NORMAN PHIPPS.

39:26.830 --> 39:28.252
WHY?

39:28.260 --> 39:30.922
I GAVE HIM A POCKET WATCH
THAT BELONGED TO MY GRANDFATHER,

39:30.930 --> 39:33.524
THE ONLY DECENT MEMBER
OF MY FAMILY.

39:33.530 --> 39:36.658
OF COURSE, HE DIED WHEN I WAS 5,
SO WHO KNOWS?

39:36.670 --> 39:39.559
STILL, KIND OF BURNS,
THINKING OF NORMAN HAVING IT.

39:39.570 --> 39:43.370
IN MY WORLD, THE WICKED
DON'T GET PARTING GIFTS.

39:53.020 --> 39:54.453
HEY, THERE, FAKE CHARLIE.

39:54.460 --> 39:57.281
YOU WEREN'T EXPECTING
TO SEE ME AGAIN, WERE YOU?

39:57.290 --> 39:59.383
CAN I COME IN?

40:01.430 --> 40:03.398
LOOK,
I WAS JUST DOING MY JOB.

40:03.400 --> 40:05.129
NONE OF IT MATTERS ANYWAY.

40:05.130 --> 40:07.064
THE MAGAZINE DROPPED THE STORY
WHEN LARRY KING SCOOPED THEM.

40:07.070 --> 40:09.959
THAT WAS THE PLAN.
I'M HERE FOR THE WATCH.

40:09.970 --> 40:11.528
EH.

40:11.540 --> 40:14.407
YOUR BOYFRIEND GOT ONE DETAIL
WRONG IN THAT INTERVIEW OF HIS.

40:15.510 --> 40:17.137
CHARLIE STONE
NEVER TALKED TO ME.

40:17.140 --> 40:19.404
I TRACKED HIM DOWN, BUT HE
WANTED TO REMAIN ANONYMOUS.

40:19.410 --> 40:21.378
THEN HOW DID YOU END UP
MEETING LOGAN?

40:21.380 --> 40:23.109
I HAD A TAP
ON CHARLIE'S PHONE.

40:23.120 --> 40:32.324
* Y-O-O-O-O-O-OU
DON'T KNOW WHO YOU ARE *

40:32.330 --> 40:34.252
THE REPORTER ACTED ALONE.

40:34.260 --> 40:38.526
HE WAS TAPPING CHARLIE'S LINE
WHEN YOU CALLED.

40:38.530 --> 40:41.966
YOUR REAL HALF-BROTHER
IS INNOCENT.

40:41.970 --> 40:45.462
* ...BET YOUR LIFE
ON A STAR *

40:45.470 --> 40:48.598
AND I WAS SO QUICK
TO BELIEVE THAT GUY.

40:50.180 --> 40:51.499
[ SNIFFLES ]

40:51.510 --> 40:54.911
AND NOW I LOOK
AT YOU AND YOUR DAD --

40:54.920 --> 40:58.242
YOU KNOW,
THAT THING THAT YOU HAVE.

40:58.250 --> 41:00.548
I NEVER HAD THAT.

41:00.550 --> 41:03.713
[ SNIFFLES ]

41:03.720 --> 41:05.950
YOU COULDN'T HAVE KNOWN.

41:05.960 --> 41:07.621
[ SIGHS ]

41:07.630 --> 41:10.497
I'M SURE
THAT DOESN'T MATTER TO HIM.

41:13.030 --> 41:19.435
* THERE'S A VOICE IN MY HEAD *

41:19.440 --> 41:22.432
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

41:22.440 --> 41:25.841
Hi, this is Charlie.
